            <h2>User Testing</h2>
          </div>
          <p>We conducted user tests at Oulu International School. After playing the game, students filled out a feedback form. The results were overwhelmingly positive, with most students enjoying the game and expressing a desire to play it again. This confirmed that our game-based approach was a viable and effective way to teach media literacy.</p>

